confirmed, ENGLISH DTS works, and sounds blinding!!!

however, some notes i observed,

firstly cannot simply run/play this dvd from PC or XBMC, i think there is an issue with the boot file.

instead either play the seperate vobs VTS_01_0.VOB through to VTS_05_1.VOB

XBMC users may have to go to audio settings (start button) to select alternate soundtrack once the VOB has been begun playback.

if using media player classic on PC, select...
menu item,     play -> filters ->   and then select an audio mode (language) to output

if using ms media players that shows the titles under "Now Playing", then it will play the dvd perfectly with menus if i select Title 7 Chapter 2 as the first file to play.
ms MP handled UK lang playback without changing any settings.

hope this helps

peace
